  masked, but it will hopefully be stable soon, before 1.4 for sure.

  16 Jul 2003; Todd Berman <tberman@gentoo.org> mono-0.25-r1.ebuild:
  libxml2-2.5.8 breaks xslt on mono, and until ! blocker deps work, masking it
  like this.

